<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>WM R. Newell., Redemption Songs 773</author>
<hymn_number>202</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kum tamtak a thawn in ka na mang,
 Ka Lal a khetden uh helo in;
 Keiding a thi ahih helo in,
 Kalvari ah.

[V2]
 Zahngaih na lien, hehpihna man bei,
 Ngaihdamna a pung keia dingin;
 Tu'n ka tha'n zalenna a mu tai,
 Kalvari ah.

[V3]
 2. A Thu ah ka gitloh na ka mu'i,
 Ka suol zieka lau leh kiling in;
 Ngaihdam ngenin Amah lam ka nga'i,
 Kalvari lam.

[V4]
 3. Tu'n ka bangkim Isu ka pie tai,
 Tu'n kipak in Lalpa'n ka nei tai;
 Ka Thagau in kipah na la sa,
 Kalvari la.

[V5]
 4. Aw Hukdamna Lampi, Hehpihna,
 Migilo te kieng a hung tung hi;
 Mangthaite Pathien in ei muta'i,
 Kalvari ah.</lyrics>
<title>AT CALVARI</title>
</song>